          "slidecontent": "• A clear statement of which AI tools are approved for use\n• Specific examples of what staff can and cannot do\n• Simple enough to read in under five minutes\n• Guidance on handling sensitive or confidential information\n• A named person or team responsible for questions and updates\n• A review date so the policy stays current"
